WEBVTT

00:01.016 --> 00:02.048
Previously on Dance Academy...

00:02.068 --> 00:06.024
Miss Webster. It's just me and you.
Prix de Fonteyn, baby.

00:06.044 --> 00:08.023
This is my chance
to be on the world stage.

00:08.044 --> 00:11.020
Showing them who I am's the only way
I'll be good enough to win.

00:14.008 --> 00:15.080
Hey, where's Sammy?
He's on right now.

00:19.040 --> 00:22.096
He was in an accident.
Sammy died on the way to hospital.

00:28.012 --> 01:12.967
