01:16.052 --> 01:17.096
They say before you die,

01:18.012 --> 01:19.084
your life flashes before your eyes.

01:22.024 --> 01:24.020
I hope so much that's true.

01:25.052 --> 01:29.084
That you get a photo album of every
moment, so you know you were here,

01:30.004 --> 01:32.000
that you were loved,
that you existed.

01:33.012 --> 01:37.020
You must need that second to prepare,
because you don't think...

01:37.040 --> 01:40.060
at least my friend didn't think
that he was going to die.

01:44.004 --> 01:46.064
So that one second
between life and death

01:46.080 --> 01:48.012
was all the time you got...

01:50.000 --> 01:51.044
to say 'goodbye'.

